South Africa’s Gill Marcus Says Credit Extension Remains ‘Subdued’

-- B y   F r a n z   W i l d
-- 
2011-05-31T19:12:19Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-31/south-africa-s-gill-marcus-says-credit-extension-remains-subdued-.html
Credit extension in  South Africa , the
continent’s biggest economy, remains “subdued,” said  Gill
Marcus , governor of the country’s  Reserve Bank , in a speech in
Johannesburg today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
